---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---
<Base
  title="Holiday Homes JBR Dubai 2026 — From AED 280/night"
  description="Find budget holiday homes at JBR Dubai from AED 280/night. Beachfront apartments with sea views. Perfect for families and short stays."
>
<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal to-navy text-white py-12 px-4 text-center">
  <div class="text-sm text-green-200 mb-2">📍 JBR — Jumeirah Beach Residence</div>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-3">Holiday Homes JBR — From AED 280/Night</h1>
  <p class="text-green-100 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Compare furnished beachfront apartments at JBR. Sea views, pool access, and walking distance to The Walk and Bluewaters.</p>
  <a href="/get-quotes?ref=jbr-homes&type=home" class="bg-yellow-400 text-navy px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-black hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-colors inline-block">Find JBR Holiday Homes →</a>
</div>
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy">Holiday Homes at JBR</h2>
    <p>JBR is Dubai's most popular beachfront holiday home district, with over 40 residential towers offering short-term rentals. One-bedroom apartments start from AED 280/night and include beach access, pool facilities, and proximity to The Walk's restaurants and shops.</p>
    <p>JBR is connected to Dubai Marina by tram and sits directly opposite Bluewaters Island and the Ain Dubai observation wheel. For families, JBR offers a car-free beachfront promenade, multiple children's play areas, and easy access to water sports.</p>
    <p>During April peak season (Eid, Art Dubai, Boat Show), JBR prices increase 20–30%. Book at least 10 days in advance for the best rates. Monthly stays from AED 6,000–8,000 for a one-bedroom offer significant savings over nightly rates.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <a href="/holiday-homes" class="text-teal font-semibold hover:underline">← Back to all holiday home areas</a>
  </div>
</div>
</Base>
